Wikidoc is distributed under two licenses, on a per-file basis. The
SPDX expression for the project as a whole is:

    GPL-2.0-or-later AND QPL-1.0

License breakdown:

  * The odoc_wiki plugin (src/odoc_wiki/) is derived from the OCaml
    ocamldoc standard generators and is distributed under the Q Public
    License version 1.0 (see LICENSE.QPL-1.0). odoc_wiki.ml carries
    an explicit QPL-1.0 header; odoc_import.ml ships without a header
    but inherits the QPL-1.0 of the surrounding plugin.

  * The latex_of_wiki tool (src/latex_of_wiki/) is distributed under
    the GNU General Public License version 2 or later (see LICENSE.GPL-2).
    wiki_latex.ml and wiki_menulatex.ml carry explicit GPL-2-or-later
    headers and are Copyright (C) 2010 Vincent Balat. The other files
    in src/latex_of_wiki/ ship without a header but inherit the
    GPL-2-or-later of the surrounding tool.
